HEADWORD: Disgregate
<hw>Dis"gre*gate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>disgregare</ets>; <ets>dis-</ets> + <ets>gregare</ets> to collect,
fr. <ets>grex</ets>, <ets>gregis</ets>, flock or herd.]</ety> <def>To
disperse; to scatter; -- opposite of <xex>congregate</xex>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
